      • load

        public Loader load()
        Start a load command chain. This is where you begin for any request that fetches data from the datastore: gets and queries. Note that all command chain objects are immutable.
        See Also:
        Objectify.load()

      • save

        public Saver save()
        Start a save command chain. Allows you to save (or re-save) entity objects. Note that all command chain objects are immutable.
        See Also:
        Objectify.save()
